Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, php-vitexsoftware-pohoda-connector, composer
Description: Tool to check and report Pohoda mServer connectivity
 Connects to a Sormware Pohoda mServer instance and verifies connectivity,
 authentication, and basic API health. Also provides a transaction report
 generator for Pohoda accounting data.

